","audioUrl":"wbw/020_054_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50970,"position":7,"arabic":"لَـَٔايَـٰتٍۢ","translation":"অবশ্যই নিদর্শনাবলী","audioUrl":"wbw/020_054_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50971,"position":8,"arabic":"لِّأُو۟لِى","translation":"সম্পন্নদেরদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_054_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50972,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلنُّهَىٰ","translation":"বিবেক","audioUrl":"wbw/020_054_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":50973,"position":10,"arabic":"٥٤","translation":"(৫৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":55,"arabic":"۞ مِنْهَا خَلَقْنَٰكُمْ وَفِيهَا نُعِيدُكُمْ وَمِنْهَا نُخْرِجُكُمْ تَارَةً أُخْرَىٰ","translation":"out of this [earth] have We created you, and into it shall We return you, and out of it shall We bring you forth once again.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2403.mp3","surahId":20,"words":[{"id":51796,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ مِنْهَا","translation":"তা (অর্থাৎ মাটি) হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_055_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51797,"position":2,"arabic":"خَلَقْنَـٰكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের আমরা সৃষ্টি করেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/020_055_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51798,"position":3,"arabic":"وَفِيهَا","translation":"ও তার মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_055_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51799,"position":4,"arabic":"نُعِيدُكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের ফিরিয়ে আনবো আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/020_055_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51800,"position":5,"arabic":"وَمِنْهَا","translation":"এবং তার মধ্য হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_055_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51801,"position":6,"arabic":"نُخْرِجُكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের বের করবো আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/020_055_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51802,"position":7,"arabic":"تَارَةً","translation":"একবার","audioUrl":"wbw/020_055_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51803,"position":8,"arabic":"أُخْرَىٰ","translation":"আরও","audioUrl":"wbw/020_055_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51804,"position":9,"arabic":"٥٥","translation":"(৫৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":56,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ أَرَيْنَٰهُ ءَايَٰتِنَا كُلَّهَا فَكَذَّبَ وَأَبَىٰ","translation":"AND, INDEED, We made Pharaoh aware of all Our messages-but he gave them the lie and refused [to heed them].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2404.mp3","surahId":20,"words":[{"id":52339,"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/020_056_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52340,"position":2,"arabic":"أَرَيْنَـٰهُ","translation":"(ফিরআউনকে) তাকে আমরা দেখিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/020_056_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52341,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتِنَا","translation":"আমাদের নিদর্শনাবলী","audioUrl":"wbw/020_056_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52342,"position":4,"arabic":"كُلَّهَا","translation":"তা সবই","audioUrl":"wbw/020_056_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52343,"position":5,"arabic":"فَكَذَّبَ","translation":"কিন্তু সে মিথ্যারোপ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_056_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52344,"position":6,"arabic":"وَأَبَىٰ","translation":"ও অমান্য করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_056_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52345,"position":7,"arabic":"٥٦","translation":"(৫৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":57,"arabic":"قَالَ أَجِئْتَنَا لِتُخْرِجَنَا مِنْ أَرْضِنَا بِسِحْرِكَ يَٰمُوسَىٰ","translation":"He said: \"Hash thou come to drive us out of our land by thy sorcery, O Moses?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2405.mp3","surahId":20,"words":[{"id":52753,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(ফিরআউন) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/020_057_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52754,"position":2,"arabic":"أَجِئْتَنَا","translation":"\"আমাদের কাছে তুমি এসেছ কি","audioUrl":"wbw/020_057_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52755,"position":3,"arabic":"لِتُخْرِجَنَا","translation":"আমাদের তুমি বের করার জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_057_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52756,"position":4,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_057_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52757,"position":5,"arabic":"أَرْضِنَا","translation":"আমাদের দেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/020_057_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52758,"position":6,"arabic":"بِسِحْرِكَ","translation":"তোমার জাদুর বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_057_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52759,"position":7,"arabic":"يَـٰمُوسَىٰ","translation":"হে মূসা","audioUrl":"wbw/020_057_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":52760,"position":8,"arabic":"٥٧","translation":"(৫৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":58,"arabic":"فَلَنَأْتِيَنَّكَ بِسِحْرٍۢ مِّثْلِهِۦ فَٱجْعَلْ بَيْنَنَا وَبَيْنَكَ مَوْعِدًۭا لَّا نُخْلِفُهُۥ نَحْنُ وَلَآ أَنتَ مَكَانًۭا سُوًۭى","translation":"In that case, we shall most certainly produce before thee the like thereof! Appoint, then, a tryst between us and thee - which we shall not fail to keep, nor [mayest] thou -at a suitable place!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2406.mp3","surahId":20,"words":[{"id":53401,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَنَأْتِيَنَّكَ","translation":"সুতরাং আমরা তোমার কাছে অবশ্যই আসবো","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53402,"position":2,"arabic":"بِسِحْرٍۢ","translation":"জাদু নিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53403,"position":3,"arabic":"مِّثْلِهِۦ","translation":"তার অনুরূপ","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53404,"position":4,"arabic":"فَٱجْعَلْ","translation":"অতএব স্থির করো","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53405,"position":5,"arabic":"بَيْنَنَا","translation":"আমাদের মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53406,"position":6,"arabic":"وَبَيْنَكَ","translation":"ও তোমার মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53407,"position":7,"arabic":"مَوْعِدًۭا","translation":"নির্দিষ্ট সময়","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53408,"position":8,"arabic":"لَّا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53409,"position":9,"arabic":"نُخْلِفُهُۥ","translation":"তা আমরা ব্যতিক্রম করবো","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53410,"position":10,"arabic":"نَحْنُ","translation":"(না) আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53411,"position":11,"arabic":"وَلَآ","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53412,"position":12,"arabic":"أَنتَ","translation":"তুমি","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53413,"position":13,"arabic":"مَكَانًۭا","translation":"প্রান্তর","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53414,"position":14,"arabic":"سُوًۭى","translation":"সমতল\"","audioUrl":"wbw/020_058_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53415,"position":15,"arabic":"٥٨","translation":"(৫৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":59,"arabic":"قَالَ مَوْعِدُكُمْ يَوْمُ ٱلزِّينَةِ وَأَن يُحْشَرَ ٱلنَّاسُ ضُحًۭى","translation":"Answered [Moses]: \"Your tryst shall be the day of the Festival; and let the people assemble when the sun is risen high.\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2407.mp3","surahId":20,"words":[{"id":53864,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"(মূসা) বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/020_059_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53865,"position":2,"arabic":"مَوْعِدُكُمْ","translation":"\"নির্দিষ্ট সময় তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/020_059_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53866,"position":3,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","translation":"দিন","audioUrl":"wbw/020_059_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53867,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلزِّينَةِ","translation":"উৎসবের","audioUrl":"wbw/020_059_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":53868,"position":5,"arabic":"وَأَن","translation":"এবং (এও) যে","audioUrl":"wbw/020_059_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{